{"title": "A gap year could be a ticket to life-changing experiences", "tags": "opinion", "timestamp": "2023-10-05", "content": "During my undergraduate studies at the National University of Singapore medical school, I did something unexpected and unconventional \u2013 I decided to take a gap year in the middle of my studies.\nI was passionate about entrepreneurship and medical innovation, and when a serendipitous chance to join a medical start-up in Boston came along, I took a leap of faith."}